Description: source code and graph explorer (Quarkslab fork of Sourcetrail)
 NumbatUI is a fork of Sourcetrail, an interactive source explorer that lets
 you navigate code through linked graph and code views. It is designed to
 explore graph-based data generated by Numbat.
 .
 This package ships the GUI application and its indexer. The C/C++ and Python
 language indexing back-ends are disabled in this build and will be enabled in
 a future release.
